The Team

A successful project requiers people to play many roles. Some members write code or
documentation, while others are valuable as testers, submitting patches and suggestions.

The team is comprised of Members and contributers. Members have direct access to the
source of a project and actively evolve the code-base. Contributers imporve the project
through submission of patches and suggestions to the Members. The number of
Contributors to the project is unbounded. Get involved today. All contributers to the project
are greatly appreciated.
